videos.description: Toledo RB Bryant Koback takes the wide sweep in for a short touchdown and puts them up 7-0.
videos.headline: Toledo's Koback goes outside for early TD

videos.description: Toledo QB Mitchell Guadagni keeps it on the option and takes it outside for a 21-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Toledo QB fools Kentucky's defense for a 21-yard TD

videos.description: Kentucky's RB Asim Rose punches it up the gut, gets tripped but falls in for the short TD to tie the game 14-14.
videos.headline: Kentucky's Rose keeps his balance, tumbles in for short TD

videos.description: Wildcats RB Christopher Rodriguez, Jr. fumbles the ball in the end zone but Kentucky TE Justin Rigg grabs it and gets his team on the board.

videos.description: Kavosiey Smoke finds the outside edge and rides the wave all the way to the end zone for a 40-yard touchdown.
